Implemented `noscope-5zg` end-to-end in `src/refresh.rs` with strict red/green/refactor flow, committed as `395ac48`.

- Added a real refresh runtime loop API in `src/refresh.rs`:
  - `RefreshRuntimeLoop`, `RuntimeCredential`, `RuntimeScheduleEntry`
  - timer scheduling derived from `compute_refresh_at()` (`NS-048`)
  - per-credential independent state/timers (`NS-031`)
  - async tick execution via `run_once(...)` with child-lifecycle guard (`child_alive`) for AgentProcess context dependency
- Wired failure and tracking behavior:
  - refresh failure handling uses `RefreshPolicy::on_refresh_failure()` (`NS-008`, `NS-030`)
  - success/failure accounting via `RefreshTracker` (`NS-032`)
  - startup rotate warning emission via `startup(..., rotate_mode, ...)` and `rotate_mode_startup_warning()` (`NS-025`)
- Added lease classification:
  - `LeaseRefreshKind::{Renewal, Rotation}` based on token value equality
  - same value => renewal, different value => rotation (resolution `js70bxmczwq0v1tbzpewp9v21n83vzzk`)
- Added dedicated tests for each required rule plus edge cases in `src/refresh.rs` (including an allow-expiry anti-spin test discovered during “Linus review” pass).
- Ran gates successfully:
  - `cargo test`
  - `cargo clippy --all-targets -- -D warnings`
